<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="apologise-vi">apologise <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'pɒlədʒaɪz/    美 /ə'pɒlədʒaɪz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>道歉；表示歉意：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I think I’ll buy her a present and apologize.
我想给她买份礼物来赔个不是。</p><footer>2009 江西</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>apologize (to sb) for (doing) sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I apologize for not being able to join you for dinner.
很抱歉，我不能和你们一起吃饭了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>apologetic /əˌpɑːlə'dʒetɪk/ adj   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Yesterday Michael a<strong><em>_</em></strong>_ to his boss for being late.  （2008 浙江）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. apologised / apologized  </p></div>